Steel - Ludum dare #23 entry by Lupinius

After crashing on a strange, small planet made out of steel the only thing in sight is a lever. As you pull it, the planet seems to change...

Usage:
Windows binaries are available, Linux binaries might follow.
To start you need Ruby 1.9.3 and rbSFML installed to launch. To start the game use "ruby Steel.rb".
